properties.diversions:
To get to Lismore from Queensland, take the Pacific Motorway until the Bangalow Road exit, then follow Bangalow Road.

The route to Lismore from the south is unchanged.

Take the Pacific Highway and Big River Way to Grafton, then Summerland Way to Cedar Point, then Bentley Road/Kyogle Road/Casino Street to Lismore.

To get to Casino and Grafton from the north, follow the route to Lismore, then take Casino Street/Kyogle Road/Bentley Road to Cedar Point, then Summerland Way.

To get to Casino and Grafton from the south, take the Pacific Highway and Big River Way to Grafton, then Summerland Way to Casino.
